column5: Working this weekend. Temps last weekend were 65. Likely 70 now. Anybody know?
was 70.3 to 71.4 on Thursday, back on the water tomorrow for more of them there Pickerals LOL   im guessing 73 to 74 now   Hair is King
Was on a small lake yesterday just North of Fenelon and it was 71.6 most of the day. Got this one and one bigger and lost one too...
Hair is King 4.5" grub was for me...  not a hit on bucktail on the lake I was on...
73.4 was the prevalent number on both graphs today, again all fish on hair, as been the case since opener,
Lower Buckhorn was  74 on Sunday on my depth finder
